title: #803 - Vicki Barbolak
description:
Vicki Barbolak, a stand up comedian who made it into the Top 10 Finals of America's Got Talent, and the host of the "Big Girls Don't Cry" podcast, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio!
